Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是星黄泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.65,0:01:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖忍法  影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:01:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说\N那个家谱上写的戈薇是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条  你快点拿着乾之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去风雷神社
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会丢下\N戈薇姑娘一个人离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.36,0:02:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你释放出来的力量\N全部都被这把刀吸收了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是星黄泉的\N坤之刃散发出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没事吧  戈薇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘  戈薇姑娘她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  接下来要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算赔上这个女人的性命\N也想要保护那把乾之刃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第139话 升云瀑步之大决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭那把生锈的刀\N能砍得了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要救这个女人的话\N就来风雷神社吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然\N不要忘了把乾之刃也带来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下也要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只会碍事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请带我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个都先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得枫婆婆曾经说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风雷神社应该是一个\N能够封印乾坤薙刀的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他还要选择那个地方\N作为交换地点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定这是个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有时间考虑这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的不幸\N害得戈薇姑娘也被卷入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一块去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要开始进行\N乾坤薙刀的复活仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让那帮家伙接近神社
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个半妖就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭他那生锈的刀\N不是我的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  法师就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来对付那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么\N我就选那个年轻的武士咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此路不通哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你闻起来好像很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是月之青龙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来交个朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  你振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒一醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此只好这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.21,0:07:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好像一下子全都走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们快点去找犬夜叉少爷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋时  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像闪到腰了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好迷人的小屁屁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一位可爱的年轻武士耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是花之朱雀  请多指教哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰上我暗之玄武来当你的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的运气还真差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.73,0:08:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭你手上那把破刀\N还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聋了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你立刻滚开  听到了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有蚊子在叮我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付你这种家伙\N还用不着铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我说了没有用的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的身体怎么那么硬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.34,0:08:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮到我出招了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖忍法  龟甲地狱车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃不掉的\N可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有\N找女人当猎物了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要好好享受一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.67,0:09:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑…跑到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖忍法  鳞之舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖忍法  逆鳞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  我马上去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等打倒了我学之白虎再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得用风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想得逞  法师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  法师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手\N我不会把乾之刃交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖把乾之刃给我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.14,0:10:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把你那张\N可爱的脸皮剥下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摆在刀刃上当作装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会让你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  一点都不听话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么把你的脸做成壁饰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我每天早上都亲一下\N怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真看不下去  这世界全乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…再不振作的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:56.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫  好烫  好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想烫死我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢突然偷袭我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒过来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.84,0:11:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  到底是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为人类的你\N为什么会和半妖一起旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和那半妖是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要问这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一点关系都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类和妖怪之间\N是不能有爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来人类和妖怪\N终究不可能结合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为人类\N总有一天会背叛妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天你也\N会背叛那个半妖的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是一种很脆弱的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论身体  心灵都很脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.11,0:12:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很脆弱\N却总是厚颜无耻的活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以人类\N会为了保全自己而背叛别人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想应该是你误会人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟人类发生过什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的吧\N所以你才会说出这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女武士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那张画上的人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月黄泉\N你在这个地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,临  兵  斗  者  皆  阵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列  在\N月黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样\N我在这里被月黄泉封印
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而乾坤薙刀中的乾之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞到了富士山那里的北条家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坤之刃则是被镇压在白灵山\N分隔两地收了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在白灵山崩塌之时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我取回了这把坤之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以枫婆婆才说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风雷神社\N是封印乾坤薙刀的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月黄泉背叛了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还曾经说过\N要和我一起活在这世上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想月黄泉\N她一定有什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明很脆弱\N却为了想要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会背叛别人苦恼不已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的愿望就是把人类\N从这种苦恼之中解救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算要怎么拯救人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唤醒这把用222只妖怪的骨骸\N打造出来的乾坤薙刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再置人类于死地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样叫做解救人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世上最无可救药的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.42,0:14:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以唯一能解救\N人类的方法就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次看到你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就感受到你散发出来的灵力强度\N和月黄泉是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我为什么不在那里\N就把乾之刃夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还特地把你引到这里来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因就是为了\N利用你所蕴藏的灵力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来进行乾坤薙刀的复活仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量被…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被分开的乾之刃\N马上就会来到我的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋时爬上瀑步了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖忍法  龟甲碎击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再也逃不了了  半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就安心的去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的尸体我会好好安葬的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒…法师…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在担心那个女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就会让你们\N在那个世界重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  接招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎口碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道\N你能够施展什么样的法力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你现在\N已经连动都动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  你再不振作的话\N那该怎么办呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再不振作起来的话\N就什么都办不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋时  你再忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  抓住我  秋时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你跑掉的\N可爱的武士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彻底的压碎你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞刃血爪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  快点找个东西抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟…糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.76,0:18:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最好动作快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快去救戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧  秋时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾之刃飞到那神社里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  这种不祥的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在终于复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的乾坤薙刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来告诉你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾坤就是阴和阳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.87,0:19:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是天和地的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:20:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森罗万象  所有位于\N相反两极的两股巨大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用乾坤薙刀\N把这两股力量分开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将眼前所看不见的\N空间劈开的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道会怎么样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话少说  快把戈薇给放了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是很脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.83,0:20:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类是会背叛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我一定要把这片大地上\N所有的人类都消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都被吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘在那里\N不能使用风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:20:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉\N铁碎牙的妖力还没有恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切都是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我把戈薇姑娘\N卷入这么危险的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还落入那个家伙的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说那些废话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.69,0:21:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定要想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把戈薇\N从那个怪物的手中救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙又还没有恢复…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管不了那么多了\N只要有决心总会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.95,0:22:00.65,ED,,0,0,0,,如今内心充满着悲伤的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.20,0:22:16.70,ED,,0,0,0,,尽管靠着我哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:22.77,ED,,0,0,0,,I get,I get,I get,get the feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:26.30,ED,,0,0,0,,I get,I get,I get,get the dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.30,0:22:32.50,ED,,0,0,0,,就像现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.77,0:22:42.77,ED,,0,0,0,,Come my way 这点黑暗之尘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.77,0:22:50.72,ED,,0,0,0,,Come close to me 现在灯已照亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:53.82,ED,,0,0,0,,I'll be with you I'll be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.25,0:22:58.50,ED,,0,0,0,,只是简简单单的陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:04.90,ED,,0,0,0,,So Come my way
